name: EVOLs Mask - Rose
description:
EVOLs Mask - An NFT collectable backed by a Physical Mask. 

Upon collection of this piece you may redeem the physcial corresponding coloured mask, 1 mask redeemable per token. (link in unlockable content)

The Holder of this token will also be airdropped a Decentraland wearbale EVOL Mask in the colour matching your item. 

A private link to EVOLs Mask AR FIlter is also included and will be unlocked after purchase.
